      The path on <m>n+1</m> vertices (so <m>n</m> edges), just one long path. <notation>
              <usage><m>P_n</m>
              </usage>
              <description>the
      path on <m>n+1</m> vertices</description>
            </notation>

          </p>
        </li>
      </dl>
    </p>

